            <pre>GET /api/&lt;API_KEY&gt;/lights</pre>

            <p>Exemple de requête en curl:</p>
            <pre>curl "http://&lt;IP_SERVER&gt;/api/&lt;API_KEY&gt;/lights" -H "Content-Type: text/plain;charset=UTF-8"</pre>


